## The Mood

@narrator: Reading the room.

<match on="run.mood">
  <when is="happy">
    @hero: I'm glad.
  </when>
  <when is="sad">
    @hero: I'm low.
  </when>
  <otherwise>
    @hero: I feel nothing in particular.
  </otherwise>
</match>
